    <item>
      <title>Evercore 的伊曼纽尔表示，美国股市暴跌将会变得更糟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/evercore-isi-s-emanuel-says-us-stock-slump-is-going-to-get-worse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Evercore ISI 的朱利安·伊曼纽尔 (Julian Emanuel) 表示，股市在从上个月创下的历史新高回落后，正在见证下跌趋势的开始，并将持续到 2024 年剩余时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/evercore-isi-s-emanuel-says-us-stock-slump-is-going-to-get-worse</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 21:06:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cumulus 在首次报价引起愤怒后即将与贷方达成新协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/cumulus-nears-new-deal-with-lenders-after-first-offer-drew-ire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cumulus Media Inc. 即将与其部分债权人达成协议，延长超过 6.5 亿美元的债务期限，这标志着贷款人在谈判中获得了比最初提议更好的条件的胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/cumulus-nears-new-deal-with-lenders-after-first-offer-drew-ire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 20:48:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金沙称翻新工程将影响澳门今年的业绩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/sands-sales-earnings-beat-on-macau-recovery-singapore-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉斯维加斯金沙集团表示，澳门一家娱乐中心和一家酒店的翻修工程将影响今年的业绩，导致股价在盘中交易中走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/sands-sales-earnings-beat-on-macau-recovery-singapore-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 20:05:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚卡多佐表示外汇储备的变化不是因为捍卫奈拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/cardoso-says-shifts-in-fx-reserves-not-due-to-defending-naira</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚央行行长奥拉耶米·卡多佐表示，奈拉近期大幅升值是对抑制通胀政策行动的积极评价，而不是因为当局一直在干预奈拉的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/cardoso-says-shifts-in-fx-reserves-not-due-to-defending-naira</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 19:36:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>体育广播公司戴蒙德将就重组举行投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/sports-broadcaster-diamond-to-hold-vote-on-reorganization-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[钻石体育集团将就亚马逊公司支持的破产退出计划进行债权人投票，同时该广播公司试图与美国两大体育联盟谈判新的电视协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/sports-broadcaster-diamond-to-hold-vote-on-reorganization-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:54:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Jane Street 交易额达 106 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/jane-street-scores-10-6-billion-trading-haul-amid-growth-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Jane Street Group LLC 去年的净交易收入为 106 亿美元——这是证明其作为主要做市商的存在并着眼于进一步增长的众多数字之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/jane-street-scores-10-6-billion-trading-haul-amid-growth-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:45:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
