      <title>新兴市场资产反弹，国际货币基金组织会议成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/emerging-markets-selloff-pauses-as-us-dollar-consolidates-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员继续调整美联储将在更长时间内维持较高利率的预期，风险资产反弹，发展中国家货币在一周多以来首次上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/emerging-markets-selloff-pauses-as-us-dollar-consolidates-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:29:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
